To everyone<P>   The point of this post is not do the most damage possible. It is to do something every fight. One of the biggest probelems wizards have with pick up groups is the apearance that they are doing nothing during 50% of the pulls. This is a stratagy that is basically set up so you can do the most damage possible ever fight and still have mana to burn a mob down when it is needed. The Idea is that group will at least see you doing something ever fight to earn your keep and when you save there butt they will remember that instead of all the time you sat there doing nothing.<P>Was that short enough for you fuzzle  <IMG SRC="wink.gif" border="0"> I know many of my post are long winded LOL
