To Baelzharon <P>Helping other members of you group goes without saying. That is what this stratagy is designed to do, alow you to do a spacific amount of damage on each pull and still have mana to help when it is needed. If you are oom you cant help anyone.<P>I am not talking about "The spectical" stratagy. I only used that stratagy as an example of how little ppl know about the wizard class and what we are doing in combat. I think that stratagy is a cop out.<P>My stratagy is something different. It is designed to do as much damage as possible each round without going oom. It does not use lvl 1 spells, but it sometimes ueses spells from you last 1 or 2 circles of spells rather than your most current. The idea is to make some kind of contribution each pull and still have the mana you need to help fellow group members in an over pull.
