I'm a 56 Wizard on Bristlebane and this no chain-casting stuff is bull with one big exception.  Velious.  Velious has some real strange aggro issues compared to the other continents.  In places like HS or Sebilis I can come damned close to chain nuking and not get aggro.  But the case where I need to nuke to 20 percent mana are few and far between.  I usually spend my time rooting mobs for the enchanter or cleric and nuking the troublesome ones.<P>So, when it comes to nuking hard we can do it and not get the aggro if the other members of the group know their roles.<P>Sabbok<BR>56 Wizard<BR>Bristlebane
