Arlina<P>Regarding Tanks noticing you are using lower lvl spells.<P>  In this case I dont think it would be a problem. You will do enought damage every fight so that your contribution should be noticable and most of the spells you use will be the correct spells for you lvl or at most one spell circle below your lvl. Even if the tanks can recongise the spell text, and see that you are sometimes using lower lvl spells, they should also see that you are using high lvl spells as well. And when you get an over pull they should definitly notice your contribution.<P> In "the spectical" stratagy, you would have a problem if the tanks notice you are only cast lvl 1 spells.<P>In the end though I think other classes notice the wizard sitting more than they notice any spells they are casting. If you are conserned about this stratagy being confused for "the spectical" stratagy, you could alway explain what you are doing to the group as soon as you join.   <IMG SRC="wink.gif" border="0">
