Woeful,<BR>I think you've done an excellent job with this strategy.  I've been using it (adjusted for spells of the level I have access to) with great success.  The groups I've been in keep waiting for me to have to medd through a fight, and waiting, and waiting...  they've been quite impressed.  This is mana management that works.  The only time I went below 60 mana was on an overpull (no group enchanter) that I had to burn down.  The times I was at 60 was on a double pull, as I did my 16 to 20% to each. <P>It would be nice if the people who are criticizing this technique would try it for an evening.  Ego would prevent them from admitting you were right, but perhaps they'd give it a break for a while.<P>Rhian
